name: Honey Stinger Acai Pomegranate Organic Energy Gel
description:
Sting or be stung. These gels are delicious on their own, or you can mix them with water to make a great-tasting energy drink. Honey Stinger organic gels provide a different taste and texture from classic gels.Contains 95% organic ingredients.Ingredients: Organic tapioca syrup, organic honey, water, potassium citrate, natural flavour, citric acid, sodium chloride. May contain milk, eggs, soy, or shellfish products.
